{"tid":158022,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想引咎辭職，腦細想唔留我，但高層連所有同事都留我點算","createTime":"2017-03-16T03:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T01:27:15.000Z","uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b30cfb165e81eda9694893c3b287e12b96a541d","tid":158022,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:24:03.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係引咎辭職咁嚴重，不過係做左1年都習慣唔到個工作模式<br />\n不斷咁做錯d不大不小既事<br />\non99地每日都比老闆屌1次<br />\n搞到我好想辭職<br />\n其實之前已經講過3次resign，次次都比高層留<br />\n岩岩同班同事吹水，問話唔做好唔好，又個個都話唔好，留係度，得我一個熟手技工咁樣樣<br />\n唉但真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚做錯野，人工幾高都cover唔到我日日擔驚受怕今日又會比人屌d咩<br />\n灰到無offer裸辭都想照辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906433cc19517fdb818c7990c23c8282f70e2192","tid":158022,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"巴打應該自我要求好高"},{"pid":"7dd9071388ef3a94c8276280b2a2a5f38328a9ea","tid":158022,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n老世即係上司？<br />\n高層係再高級啲？"},{"pid":"4dc898c02329e57435b58cac474287aa54f5ebcd","tid":158022,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打應該自我要求好高</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係真係適應唔到呢間公司先至咁樣<br />\n日日比人屌真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c561cef33de1c4565abdfd63705209bc340caa","tid":158022,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw<br />\n老世即係上司？<br />\n高層係再高級啲？</blockquote><br />\n定係最大嗰個老闆唔留？<br />\nsor<br />\n理解不能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08da592ef4d7a40a69b9202be9da460434550cf","tid":158022,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:27:58.000Z